                  "display": "Admission evaluation note"
                }
              ]
            },
            "title": "Admission evaluation"
          },
          {
            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">On April 23, 2025, a fixateur externe was applied to stabilize the fracture. The procedure was performed under general anesthesia without complications.<table class=\"hl7__hdr\"><thead><tr><th>Procedures</th><th>SNOMED</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Application of external fixator device, Left lower limb</td><td>304527002</td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
            },
            "entry": [
              {
